Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.27,0:25:52.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}状況は非科学的に
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.94,0:25:56.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情のモンタージュ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.82,0:25:59.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}誰が誰を呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.62,0:26:05.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向けば　逃げてく視線　感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.50,0:26:07.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気のせいじゃつれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.83,0:26:12.88,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}アンテナは才能って言うでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.38,0:26:16.76,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}だってだって　知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.01,0:26:18.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君は違うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.59,0:26:25.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}青春の温度差　今のうち　正してあげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.27,0:26:29.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}明日解決するなら　今でもよくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.85,0:26:35.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君のミステリー　解いてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.57,0:26:40.11,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}少年の秘密めいた背中探せ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.28,0:26:43.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今日も君はファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.91,0:26:47.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惹けれてゆくよ　ずるい
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.66,0:26:53.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨らんだ好奇心　トリックはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.46,0:26:57.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気になるよ　興味深い
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.80,0:27:00.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.27,0:25:52.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}状况完全不科学
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.94,0:25:56.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情如拼贴画般交织
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.82,0:25:59.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}是谁在将谁呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.62,0:26:05.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}回头时感觉到你逃避的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.50,0:26:07.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}说这是错觉未免无情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.83,0:26:12.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}直觉该称为才能才对
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.38,0:26:16.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}因为我想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.01,0:26:18.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}难道你并非如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.59,0:26:25.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在就为你纠正青春的温差
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.27,0:26:29.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}既然明天能解决 不如趁现在搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.85,0:26:35.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我想要解开你的悬疑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.57,0:26:40.11,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}探寻少年神秘的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.28,0:26:43.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天的你也如同幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.91,0:26:47.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狡猾地吸引着我不断沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.66,0:26:53.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨胀的好奇中分明不含心机
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.46,0:26:57.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人在意 耐人寻味
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.80,0:27:00.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}这究竟是为什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很感激你这么难得为我做便当
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是老姐啊 为什么你做的是民族料理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看店辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 赢了赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然赢得很险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜获得优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 都是多亏了折木同学帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真是吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为要让奉太郎做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非地球人全死光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是被祭典的气氛感染了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有东西想让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLiBian-S02\fs60\c&H121E1D&\3c&HE9F1F3&\pos(930,771)}料理研已失去圆勺  十文字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:38.51,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,300)\blur3\pos(1410,878)}十文字事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 圆勺被偷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 只有我们组的被偷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有人很闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是料理研
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围棋部和无伴奏合唱部好像也发生了同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占卜研也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下了一张同样格式的…犯罪声明…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有人闲得发慌啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这调料的香味也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往常的那个 千反田爱琉的好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要发动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁在文化祭时做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会写着十文字同学的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他要接二连三地偷东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很在…意…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是做这种事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些文集…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些文集——呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是在普通活动上宣传 我估计也卖不了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得做些更引人注意的事才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个怪盗事件卖给墙报部怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好还能上明天的校内广播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到这样的话 文集也会变得畅销起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个主意真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说卖 要怎么卖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个事件和古典部又没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:03:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「古典部的名侦探折木奉太郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「将揪出扰乱文化祭的怪盗十文字」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「关于他此前活跃的英姿」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「就请在古典部的文集『冰菓』中欣赏吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个点子太妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 倒是不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样既可以揪出十文字 还可以宣传古典部…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么名侦探啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揽客吉祥物这种事我坚决不干！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试着努力一下嘛 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我愿意当这个小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是光学生就有一千多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上普通游客 人数还会更多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多人 要我怎么找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是根本办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怪盗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是把古典部也当作目标就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就自导自演…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开 开玩笑的啦 玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他之前偷了哪几个社团的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围棋部 无伴奏合唱部 料理研 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占卜研
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？无伴奏合唱部 围棋部 占卜研 料理研吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ABC！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 铃木吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E开头的社团有电影研 园艺部 话剧部 SF部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}有社团丢东西吗 对 盗窃案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是吗 没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这其中是有规律的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是非常简单的规律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无伴奏合唱部 围棋部 占卜研
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.87,50,NTP,0,490,0,,あ{\c&HFFFFFF&}かぺら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.87,50,NTP,150,0,0,,い{\c&HFFFFFF&}ご
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.87,50,NTP,550,0,0,,う{\c&HFFFFFF&}らない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过一个字母 然后是料理研
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.20,50,NTP,530,0,0,,お{\c&HFFFFFF&}りょうり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再出现E开头的社团就可以确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.54,50,NTP,0,400,0,,え
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是五十音序吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,园艺部中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人在的一会儿时间里 水枪被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是烤白薯的时候灭火用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天有个客人是园艺部的 他就带着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂的ABC谋杀案里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是名字首字母人为A的人在地名首字母为A的地方被杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理研是圆勺被偷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.27,50,NTP,0,470,0,,お{\c&HFFFFFF&}りょうり
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.27,50,NTP,90,0,0,,お{\c&HFFFFFF&}たま
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同学 你问过占卜研被偷了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 有的 是「命运之轮」的塔罗牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.57,50,NTP,55,0,0,,う{\c&HFFFFFF&}んめいのわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:38.58,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,264)}无伴奏合唱部→(饮料)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:38.58,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,402)}围棋部→(棋子)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:38.58,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\b0\c&H578285&\3c&HC4EFF2&\an1\pos(622,543)}占卜研→(命运之轮)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:38.58,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,693)}园艺部→(水枪)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:38.58,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,843)}料理研→(圆勺)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,园艺部的水枪是AK吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.25,50,NTP,0,470,0,,え{\c&HFFFFFF&}んげい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.25,50,NTP,400,0,0,,え{\c&HFFFFFF&}いけい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AK？那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯产的自动步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样倒说得通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围棋部就是石头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.59,50,NTP,0,400,0,,い{\c&HFFFFFF&}ご
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.59,50,NTP,270,0,0,,い{\c&HFFFFFF&}し
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那无伴奏合唱部…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都无所谓 只要一查马上就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人的署名是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十文字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这么念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般念起来是「十个字」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.52,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：里志等人用的是「十文字」作为姓氏的念法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 十个字！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 A I U E O KA KI KU KE KO总共十个字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,0,800,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}あ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,0,710,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,0,620,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,0,530,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}え
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,0,440,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}お
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,0,280,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,0,130,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}き
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,70,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}く
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,250,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}け
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.53,50,NTP,400,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}こ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 最后一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是古典部！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.95,50,NTP,35,0,0,,こ{\c&HFFFFFF&}てん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不觉得 这个材料已经足够推销古典部了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上到墙报部去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然想到了一点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 算了 我去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊原你不回漫研吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼什么哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我待在这里不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没生气！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈判的窍门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 要让对方觉得自己备受期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二 让自己的利益显得小一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三 在没有人的地方拜托异性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 我去园艺部采访了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 无伴奏合唱部怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在打电话问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}也要向料理研确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}对 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}要我说几遍才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}有时间闲聊还不如快点行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 千反田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以请你过后再来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的 那就之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于古典部的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事 我不是说了要有特别的话题…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有这样的话题了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来听听？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我时间很紧 麻烦你简短…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…喂 你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事 我只能找墙报部商量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是吗 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这事对古典部也没多大好处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 有点想帮忙的感觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我不懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了吧 现在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有话题的话就过后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 关于话题的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在文化祭上偷了很多社团的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个犯人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十文字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是十文字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 五十音序吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然连占卜研也中招了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这儿是墙报部嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.35,50,NTP,220,0,0,,か{\c&HFFFFFF&}べしんぶん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美工刀被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.27,50,NTP,0,215,0,,か{\c&HFFFFFF&}ったーないふ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在很忙就是因为这事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 虽然很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我在等的就是这样的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 真亏你能注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 是折木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远垣内学长 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都告诉你这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请报道一下古典部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后又强调一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就和怀疑远垣内学长没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 有成果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…嗯 不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我在自言自语而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 先不说这个 我去无伴奏合唱部打听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.12,50,NTP,245,0,0,,あ{\c&HFFFFFF&}かぺら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说被偷的是苹果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.21,50,NTP,400,0,0,,あ{\c&HFFFFFF&}っぷるじゅーす
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也从墙报部听说 他们的美工刀被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到KA了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是五十音序没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 下一个KI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有魔术部了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.06,50,NTP,100,0,0,,き{\c&HFFFFFF&}じゅつ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术部的下一场公演就快开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要到那里去埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能当场抓住犯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这是这类怪盗的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会被自己的规则所束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揭穿十文字的真身并不困难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 如果在KI的时候就被揭穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人就没法找上古典部了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事总有办法解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是这样 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我到魔术部去埋伏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.01,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(1100,178)\blur2}秋 分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.01,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,342)\blur2}昼夜等长日 乃是秋分时
